<p><a name="Further_reading" id="Further_reading"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Thales&amp;action=edit&amp;section=20" title="Edit section: Further reading">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Further reading</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Morse, Sidney H.; Marvin, Joseph B., <a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=kIAQAAAAIAAJ&amp;pg=PA170&amp;lpg=PA170&amp;dq=thales+sound+mind+in+sound+body&amp;source=bl&amp;ots=73Il9ErYW3&amp;sig=Bdpml5rYncGWPcq8y1AqYoSRy7c#PPA170,M1" class="external text" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=kIAQAAAAIAAJ&amp;pg=PA170&amp;lpg=PA170&amp;dq=thales+sound+mind+in+sound+body&amp;source=bl&amp;ots=73Il9ErYW3&amp;sig=Bdpml5rYncGWPcq8y1AqYoSRy7c#PPA170,M1" rel="nofollow"><i>The Radical</i></a>, A. Williams &amp; Co., 1868. Cf. p.170 and on.</li>
</ul>
